I Am Currently Working On A Server Called Airscape We Will Have 2 Worlds, We Could Use 1 With A Higher Max Poplution Sence The Server Will Run Off A Run Off A Dedicated Server but We Will Discuss That Later, The Base Is Off Testscape I Have Currently Fixed A Few Bugs And Added Reputation System (credits meiscooldude) And Weapon Deleys Fixed, But Anyways Lets Get To The Point I Need A Team Of Coders, The Current Project Is To Add Shops, Quest, And Npc Drops Any Good Coders (THAT ARE NOT FIRST TIME POSTERS) May Join This Project Is Going To Be Big And One Of The Best.
